explanation: Uses dynamic programming with two arrays: len[i] stores the length of the longest increasing subsequence ending at i, and cnt[i] stores the count of such sequences. For each i, iterate over all previous indices j to update len and cnt. Finally, sum counts for indices with length equal to the global maximum.

